company.name: Gen Digital Inc. Contingent Value Rights

metadata.companyName: Gen Digital Inc. Contingent Value Rights
metadata.description: GENVR represents Contingent Value Rights (CVRs) issued by Gen Digital Inc. as part of its acquisition of MoneyLion. Each CVR entitles the holder to receive a contingent payment of $23.00 in Gen common stock if Gens average volume-weighted average share price reaches at least $37.50 over 30 consecutive trading days within 24 months following the closing of the transaction.
